    * {

    .error {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100vh;
      background: url('data:image/png;base64,') no-repeat right bottom;
      background-size: 130%;

    @media screen and (min-width: 768px) {
      .error {
        background-size: 65%;

    .error .container {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 800px;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .error .image {

      top: -20px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);

    .error .image svg {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
    }
    .error h1 {
      font-size: 20vw;
      line-height: 1.2;
      color: #e91d38;
      font-weight: 900;
    }
    .error p {
      font-size: max(16px, 2vw);
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: 200;
    }
  </style>
